events.title: Community Hours
events.description: Join us on Tuesday, from 1 pm to 5 pm, during our weekly community hours at IR. The space is open for work, meetings, and intimate weekday programs. WiFi, a growing book collection, and tea are all provided. No RSVP required, stop by and say hi!
